<h1>About <a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf">https://www.w3.org/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf</a></h1>

<form action="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,tools" method="get">
<p>
 <label id="uri-label" for="uri">Enter another URI:</label>
 <input id="uri" name="uri" type="text" size="60" value="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf" />
</p>
</form>

<h2>Administrative pages</h2>

<p>
The following W3C administrative information is available about
"<a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf">https://www.w3.org/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf</a>".
Some of these pages can also be accessed by adding the comma suffix shown to the document Web address &mdash; these so called <em>"comma-tools"</em> work on any <code>www.w3.org</code> page.
</p>

<table>
<thead>
<tr>
  <th>For this page</th>
  <th>General tool</th>
  <th>,shortcut</th>
  <th>Access control</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
  <!-- only show if public -->
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,text">A plain text version of the page,
  handy for pasting into email.</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="/services/html2txt">HTML to Text converter</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,text</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,checklink">List of bad links in the page</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://validator.w3.org/checklink">Link Checker</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,checklink</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>


<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,rchecklink">Bad links in a page and in pages linked from it</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://validator.w3.org/checklink">Link Checker</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,rchecklink</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,validate">List of HTML markup errors.</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://validator.w3.org/">HTML Validator</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,validate</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,spell">List of spelling errors.</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://www.w3.org/2002/01/spellchecker">W3C Spellchecker</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,spell</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,cssvalidate">List of style CSS errors.</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://jigsaw.w3.org/css-validator/">CSS Validator</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,cssvalidate</td>
  <td class="desc">Works only on public pages.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
 <td class="tool"><a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,i18n">List of internationalisation errors.</a></td>
 <td class="desc"><a href="https://validator.w3.org/i18n-checker/">i18n checker</a></td>
 <td class="shortcut">,i18n</td>
 <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>
<tr>
 <td class="tool"><a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,source">Source of this document (e.g. CVS repository, proxy, redirect).</a></td>
 <td class="desc">Web tree source info</td>
 <td class="shortcut">,source</td>
 <td class="desc">Public</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <!-- If it is a "file" -->
  <td class="tool"> <a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,cvslog">Log of changes to the document</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://cvs.w3.org/Team/">CVS Log</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,cvslog</td>
  <td class="desc">Team-only</td>
</tr>
<tr>
 <td class="tool"><a href="https://www.w3.org/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,pubrules">Check the compliance of  this document</a> to the <a href="https://www.w3.org/pubrules/">W3C publication rules</a></td>
 <td class="desc"><a href="https://www.w3.org/pubrules/">the pubrules checker</a></td>
 <td class="shortcut">,pubrules</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,minutes">Generate formatted minutes of a meeting IRC log</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="/2005/02/minutes">Online Minutes Generator</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,minutes</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,diff">Open the diff form</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://services.w3.org/htmldiff">HTML diff tool</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,diff</td>
  <td class="desc">Same as the document</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>


<h2>Public services</h2>

<p>These are provided by various sites.</p>

<table>
<thead>
<tr>
  <th>Service</th>
  <th>Provider</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
  <!-- only show if public -->
  <td class="tool"><a
  href="https://redbot.org/?uri=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.w3.org%2FWAI%2FER%2Ftests%2Fxhtml%2Ftestfiles%2Fresources%2Fpdf%2Fdummy.pdf">HTTP and caching data about this resource</a></td>
  <td class="desc"> <a
  href="https://github.com/mnot/redbot/">REDbot</a></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

<h2>Team access only</h2>

<table>
<thead>
<tr>
  <th>For this page</th>
  <th>General tool</th>
  <th>,shortcut</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
  <td class="tool">
  <!-- only show the appropriate one -->
    <a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,access">Access control for file</a> or
    <a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf*,access">directory</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="/Systems/Acl/UserDoc">Access Control</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">.../file,access or .../dir/*,access</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,new">List all templates in this directory</a></td>
  <td class="desc">Simple templating system: <a href="/2003/08/template-usage">manual</a>, <a href="https://cvs.w3.org/Team/WWW/Systems/Http/cgi-bin/new/">source</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,new</td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,ls">Browse Web space</a></td>
  <td class="desc">List of files and directories under the current directory in Web space <a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,ls">with icons</a> or <a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,dir">with dates/sizes</a> (<a href="https://cvs.w3.org/Team/WWW/2021/05/view-gallery/">source</a>)</td>
  <td class="shortcut">,ls<br>,dir</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <!-- If it is a "file" -->
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,mirror">Status of this resource on various mirrors</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://www.w3.org/Systems/Mirroring/">Mirroring</a></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,mirror</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,pdf">PDF rendering of this page</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="/Team/html2pdf">Generate a PDF for a given
  URL.</a> “,pdf” generates pages suitable for A4 paper, “,pdfl” for
  US Letter paper, and “,pdfui” opens a form to adjust the
  parameters. (<a
  href="https://cvs.w3.org/Team/WWW/Systems/Http/cgi-bin/html2pdf/">source</a>)</td>
  <td class="shortcut">,pdf<br>,pdfl<br>,pdfui</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="tool"><em>n/a</em></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="https://www.w3.org/Systems/Mail/annotations">Mark messages as spam</a>
  in <a href="https://lists.w3.org/">W3C's mailing list archives</a> (apply to 
  URIs on <code>lists.w3.org</code>)</td>
  <td class="shortcut">,spam</td>
</tr>

<tr>
  <td class="tool"><a href="/WAI/ER/tests/xhtml/testfiles/resources/pdf/dummy.pdf,shorten">Shorten this URI</a></td>
  <td class="desc"><a href="/2012/shorten/">URI Shortener</a><br /><small>Redirection service to shorten a long w3.org uri into a more convenient one, eg <a href="https://w3.org/brief/1">https://w3.org/brief/1</a>. Should not be used for high volume requests.</small></td>
  <td class="shortcut">,shorten</td>
</tr>

</tbody>
</table>

